{"tid":2069783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國難五金屌咖喱飯派富臨糉","createTime":"2020-06-18T15:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T10:01:38.000Z","uid":148315,"like":385,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"342f8536cf88fddbf3c9766a05ff8ce45e99c6d5","tid":2069783,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fOZVJU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfOZVJU4.png&h=305c571a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅主要論點係派藍店糉會影響黃店糭生意<br />\n因為啲人拎咗糭就唔會再買糭<br />\n<br />\n泛民大把嘢可以屌<br />\n但講真我覺得派藍店糭係利大於弊<br />\n一來「蛇齋餅糭」有「糭」已經證明派糭確實係拉廢老票常用而且有效嘅手段<br />\n二來佢都有用貼紙遮<br />\n<br />\n因為拎得糭嘅多數係廢老<br />\n所以本身受眾唔多人係堅持去黃店消費嘅一群<br />\n更何況絕大部份人要食糭都唔會淨係拎一兩隻糭就夠喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不論黃藍陣營嘅人一定會自己再買糭（自己包除外）<br />\n<br />\n同埋講咗好耐 抗爭講咩風骨<br />\n對自己陣營利大於弊嘅就拎/做 利益最大化"},{"pid":"6d162cf4fe1e265592ba398b0722a16a893efbc7","tid":2069783,"uid":174432,"like":248,"dislike":7,"score":241,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"重有人理佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55f15ed32966075df3e4be19291a2f544f7a517","tid":2069783,"uid":1049,"like":338,"dislike":8,"score":330,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"國難五金收皮啦，個隻熱狗格摵都摵唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之批鬥同路人最大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b43405144dd1e8d18a2d350213b1329dec736c","tid":2069783,"uid":21545,"like":198,"dislike":3,"score":195,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"人哋送嚟 唔通唔要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0215c1364d7862bb730d9bb473e336c6b7e9df27","tid":2069783,"uid":28485,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"佢咁講區議員嘜7都啦應該派啦<br />\n派完啲街坊就唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im