Q4：將抗爭者的故事出書賺暴利，食人血饅頭！<br />\nA4：本舖會秉持一貫宗旨，在能力範圍內能夠應付的產品以學生優惠價出售。這亦是為何被抄家三次亦能全身而退，因我們有收錢賣貨，即使有些時候是完全不符市場定價的十元套餐，但我們亦有被視為人血饅頭的VIP產品以取暴利。為了不會誤中「非法集資」的法網下，本店沒有收取過任何贊助，那大家想一想為何本店能推出數以千計的「學生餐」。<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n圖文：手機中看到RTHK今日的即時新聞，以證明家書原稿於此時已不在皇軍手中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hKmdyov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhKmdyov.jpg&h=0537fba3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eac1fef0c5b35b56b77f2ddb80866fc256fc2e29","tid":2069783,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 人血饅頭"},{"pid":"9de2a76384384f1f4f51b16da9cb20a53187209e","tid":2069783,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08d33e44a1a9d6f8a0f205fcc29be72c08eb38b","tid":2069783,"uid":318505,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T18:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔係佢地主動派藍糭<br />\n係煤氣公司應承sponsor，要派個陣先知係富撚糭<br />\n<br />\n人地10號已經講緊有sponsor<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Ftb2wc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ftb2wc.png&h=f6a7bc9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXZq6XT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXZq6XT.jpg&h=1b81b76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打後人人都係呢個星期先知係富撚<br />\n想點？想人丟曬啲糭？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Wb1Fg0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Wb1Fg0.png&h=7049098a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uutjrW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuutjrW2.png&h=5764f754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYHkboJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYHkboJ.png&h=d405b843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫熱狗慳啲啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iEMQyCj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l